description: Open house canceled. 110 D St is a large single family ideally located on private lot a short walk from South Boston's brand new Washington Village mixed-use development, Andrew T Station, South Boston's waterfront and beaches. 3 Bed + Office/4th Bed, 2.5 bath. Main level features a large living room and kitchen. Private deck off kitchen perfect for BBQs and entertaining. 1/2 Bath also on main level. Second level has a large guest bedroom, full bath and SECOND living room that could be transformed into a 4th bedroom, office or study. Third level has a second full bath and two large bedrooms. Full basement with washer/dryer and tons of room for storage. Property is perfect for occupant who wants to transform interior into a luxurious primary residence or investor looking for a stand-alone cash flowing 4 bedroom rental. Parking is private and on site (parking area is owned by 3rd party). Easy to show! 24 hour notice required.
